The teacher in the lesson:
- Children, tell me which part of my body you like and I will tell you who you will be when you grow up.
The boy Petya:
- I like your eyes.
The teacher:
- Of course, Petya will be our optometrist.
The boy Kolya:
- I like your teeth.
The teacher:
- Of course, Kolya will become a dentist.
The girl Masha:
- I like your hair.
The teacher:
- Everything is also clear, Masha will become a hairdresser.
- And that Vovochka is silent today?
Vovochka gets up and says:
- As I understand it, I will work at the dairy!
